Use the standard library
This is how to is_bored of S:
   Remember that text is S
   When isarray of S, then:
      Remember that text is ""
      Remember that n is S's length
      Remember that i is 0
      Do this n times:
         Add text to item i in S
         Increase i
      End do
   End when
   Remember that bored is 0
   When find of text and "bored" is not (diff of 0 and 1), then:
      Remember that bored is 1
   End when
   The answer is bored
